Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear the sound of the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See the deep blue of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amid hollow days, permeated by the invisible smell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of an unending summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I met a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with eyes like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so it began.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I just... don't want to go.{lit: Don't wanna go.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Family outing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a hot one today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I gotta hit up the shop.{TLC: konbini} {ED: Potentially too fast but there isn't a great alt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll grab a drink too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The grief...{alt: The sad things.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pain...{alt: The painful things.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It brings them all back fresh to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish summer would just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}be over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:56.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think there's something in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fish, maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems too big, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:22.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so deep and clear...
Comment: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so deep and clear...
Comment: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's fine to gaze at the sea,{lit: It's fine to be captivated by the sea,}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:34.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but it's not safe to lean over like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:40.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't have fallen in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I apologize, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,For a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought you were preparing to throw yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're the only one—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but don't be so rude.{alt: but please don't be rude.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to offend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning, Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}sooooo{\i0} sorry I couldn't walk with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What happened? You slept in?
Comment: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Comment: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You slept in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:01.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nah, uh... I forgot to leave my uniform out to dry\Nbefore passing out last night.
Comment: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nah, uh...
Comment: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I passed out without leaving my uniform out to dry last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I ended up drying it \Nwith a hairdryer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Totally didn't think I'd make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You still have that cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But let's not talk about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Was everything okay this morning?!{alt: Were you okay by yourself this morning?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You didn't get hassled\Nby any creeps, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not a helpless little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko, you're still doing this?{alt: Miko, you're at it again?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're seriously {\i1}so{\i0} protective of Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako's kinda disaster-prone, so I worry.{alt: She's always getting herself into trouble, so I worry.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, \Nshe tripped over nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:45.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's true! She's always tripping over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I get how you feel, Miko, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You sure?{alt: Really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning! Back to your seats, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, my heart...{lit: My heart...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sank deep...{sank deep into the sea on that day}{lit: Ever since that day...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it's lain at the bottom of the sea ever since.{and it's lain there ever since.}{lit: it's been sunk at the\Nbottom of the sea...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:39.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}think she was like the sea? {TODO}
Comment: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}think she was like the sea?
Comment: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you see Mikarin's video?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I totally did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hilarious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We've got sectionals{alt: electives} today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I hope I can keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Aw crap, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a message from the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:08.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Today's student council officer meeting will begin at 4:45 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can we stop by the bookstore on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And the corner store! \NThey've got new pastries!{konbini}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! \NI thought you'd left already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:23.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ms. Takano made some \Nmath worksheets for the classes you missed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and she wants you to come back to do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat!{optional line}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,B-But I was about to head out with Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Yamashita wants you to go to his office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,after you're done with the worksheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,H-Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate worksheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:54.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And I just {\i1}know{\i0} Mr. Yamashita's gonna chew me out for skipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It'll only get worse \Nif you don't go sort it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you\Ntill you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:03.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll finish up lickety-split, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Pull down the skirt hem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Take off the choker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hinako!\N Wait here, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I'll have to find \Na place to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A classroom? Nothing to do there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could go to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll read a book until Miko comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound of waves crashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I recognize it from this morning.{lit: From... this morning...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still in my school slippers.{alt: indoor shoes}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miko might be done by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...{alt: There you are, girl. Found you at last.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,y... ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,y... ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mmm, you smell so good...{alt: Ohh... what a sweet aroma.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
