Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:48.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was interrupted this morning, but now I'll finally have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:00.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of a sudden...
Comment: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just all of a sudden...
Comment: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh...
Comment: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}finally join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,it wasn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's a mermaid doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And how dare you stop me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This miserable iso-onna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iso-onna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You sure have a lot to say \Nfor such a bottom-feeding{weak?} yokai.
Comment: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You speak so boldly for such a low-level yokai.
Comment: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is {\i1}my{\i0} prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:39.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like a scene from hell itself.
Comment: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like a scene from hell itself.
Comment: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:45.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was paralyzed by the unfolding atrocity.
Comment: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was paralyzed by the unfolding atrocity, and yet...
Comment: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:12.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:21.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you for so long!
Comment: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd been looking for you for so long!
Comment: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,For me? Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your flesh and blood is especially delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's what draws creatures like her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart began to race...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Pathetic creatures with no sense of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:49.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deafening, like the pounding of the waves.
Comment: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deafening, like the pounding of the waves.
Comment: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But you're going to become more delicious still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:57.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So until then, I'll make sure...{alt: So until that day, I will}
Comment: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So until then,
Comment: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to keep you safe.
