Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!{alt: Hot enough for you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:56.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako?! What... Why are you wet all over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:01.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was fussing over me a lot yesterday after everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:05.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could that have brought her cold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miko's surprisingly delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So rude! {Says the same thing as in the sign here}{TLC: doesn't need to be same if you have time to read both}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope it doesn't get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Gonna be another scorcher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wanna hit the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's grab something to eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Will you really eat me?{alt: really eat me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I won't eat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:57.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Be sure to look after those wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll see you again.
