Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Man, where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
