Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:45.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that she was going to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why did she just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:57.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning! Back to your seats, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:01.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah. Before homeroom starts, let me introduce our transfer student.
