Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be joining our class starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the tide... the sea...{alt: Of the sea...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oumi Shiori.{alt: Please welcome Oumi Shiori.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came here to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she could
